{"word":"犴","detail":[{"title":"基本字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"犴"},{"type":"span","content":"hānㄏㄢˉ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 驼鹿。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"犴"},{"type":"span","content":"ànㄢˋ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 〔狴"},{"type":"span","content":"犴","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"〕见“"},{"type":"a","content":"狴"},{"type":"text","content":"”。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 〔"},{"type":"span","content":"犴","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"狱〕古代乡亭的牢狱，引申为狱讼之事。亦作“岸狱”。"}]]},{"title":"英文翻译","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"a wild dog, a not very large lock-up"}]]},{"title":"详细字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"犴"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"àn","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈名词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1) 产于中国北方的一种野狗,似狐而小,黑喙"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"犴,胡地野狗也。——《说文》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"犴,野狗,似狐,黑喙。——《字林》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2) 古时乡亭的拘留所,后泛指监狱"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"狱犴不治。——《荀子·宥坐》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(3) 又如:犴户(犴庭,犴圄,犴狴,犴狱。皆指监狱);犴讼(狱讼)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(4)  另见 "},{"type":"span","content":"hān","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}]]},{"title":"基本词义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"犴"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"hān","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}],[{"type":"span","content":"〈名词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)  即驼鹿。产于欧洲和亚洲的现存世上最大的一种鹿( Alces alces ),鼻长如骆驼,雄的有角,角上部呈铲形。分布于中国东北以及蒙古和俄罗斯等地。亦称“麋”、“犴达罕”、“堪达罕”"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2)  另见 "},{"type":"span","content":"àn","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "}]]},{"title":"康熙字典","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【巳集下】【犬字部】犴 ·康熙筆画：7　·部外筆画：3 "}],[{"type":"text","content":"【廣韻】【正韻】俄寒切【集韻】俄干切，"},{"type":"span","content":"𠀤"},{"type":"text","content":"音雃。【廣韻】本作豻。北地野狗，似狐而小。【正字通】陸佃曰：黑喙，善守。故字從干。干，扞也。【淮南子·道應訓】靑犴白虎。　又【集韻】【韻會】"},{"type":"span","content":"𠀤"},{"type":"text","content":"何干切，音寒。本亦作豻。義同。　又【集韻】居寒切，音干。野犴，獸名。　又【唐韻】五旰切【集韻】【正韻】魚旰切【韻會】疑旰切，"},{"type":"span","content":"𠀤"},{"type":"text","content":"音岸。【說文】豻，或从犬。引《詩》宜犴宜獄。今《詩·小雅》作宜岸宜獄。【釋文】《韓詩》作犴。鄕亭之繫曰犴，朝廷曰獄。【後漢·崔駰傳】獄犴塡滿。　又人名。【左傳·昭二十四年】越大夫胥犴，勞王于豫章之汭。【史記·梁孝王世家】睢陽人類犴反者。【註】人姓名也。反字或作友。【集韻】本作豻，野犬也。犬所以守，故謂獄爲豻。◎按《廣韻》犴，獄也。豻，野狗也。分二義。《集韻》本《說文》合爲一。應從《集韻》。　又【集韻】【類篇】"},{"type":"span","content":"𠀤"},{"type":"text","content":"魚撊切，音鴈。本作干。或作"},{"type":"span","content":"𤜵"},{"type":"text","content":"。　又居莧切，音襇。逐虎犬。亦作"},{"type":"span","content":"𤜵"},{"type":"text","content":"。"},{"type":"span","content":"𤜵"},{"type":"text","content":"原字从幵。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"考證：〔【正字通】陸仙曰，黑喙，善守。故字從干。干，扞也。〕　謹按黑喙云云出陸佃埤雅，仙改佃。〔【史記·梁平王世家】睢陽人類犴反者〕　謹照原文平王改孝王。 "}]]},{"title":"字源演变","content":[]},{"title":"同音字","content":[]}],"type":"通用字","pinyin":["àn","hān"],"radical":"犭","stroke":"三画","total_stroke":"六画","t_radical":"犬","t_stroke":"三画","t_total_stroke":"六画","stroke_order":"ノフノ一一丨","input_method":{"bopomofo":"KHMJ","number":"41240","unicode":"U+72B4","wubi":"QTFH"}}